[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0888","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0888.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0817","title":"Lynx 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Lynx WWW 客户端在处理 telnet 等协议时，会调用外部程序处理请求，但未对传入的命令行参数进行有效过滤，导致远程攻击者可通过构造特制的 URL 链接，向 Lynx 传递恶意命令行参数，从而在用户系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多个 Lynx 版本，危害等级严重，攻击者可通过诱使用户点击恶意链接完成利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0817"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.183","remediation":"升级到 Lynx 2.8.1 及以上版本，该版本修复了传递不可信参数给外部程序（如 telnet）的问题。如无法升级，可在 Lynx 配置中将 `TRUSTED_LYNXCGI` 和 `ALLOW_USER_OPTIONS` 设为关闭，并禁用对外部协议处理程序的自动调用作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0817"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0888.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0887","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0887.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1033","title":"Microsoft Outlook Express POP3 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook Express 4.72.3612.1700 之前版本存在 POP3 协议处理缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含特殊构造的 \"..\" 字符串的恶意邮件，诱使 Outlook 重新进入 POP3 命令模式，导致 POP3 会话挂起无法继续处理后续邮件，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Outlook Express 4.27.3110 及 4.72.3120 等版本，攻击者无需认证即可触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1033"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.953","remediation":"将 Microsoft Outlook Express 升级至 4.72.3612.1700 或更高版本，此版本修复了包含 \"..\" 序列的恶意邮件导致 POP3 命令模式循环挂起的问题。如无法升级，建议禁用 POP3 邮箱功能或改用 IMAP 协议收信作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92647407427342&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92663402004275&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/252","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19207","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1033.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1033","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/e7c7a6140bbd6a60ea622b6124620fbed9d12332/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1033.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-935q-jf44-fq38/GHSA-935q-jf44-fq38.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0887.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0886","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0886.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1031","title":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 counter.exe 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 版本的 counter.exe 组件存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向该程序发送超长参数，触发缓冲区处理异常，导致目标程序挂起（hang），无法正常响应后续请求。该漏洞仅需网络可达即可触发，无需身份认证，攻击门槛低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1031"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.700","remediation":"升级 Behold Web Page Counter 至 2.71 或更高版本。如厂商已停止维护，建议部署 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）过滤超长请求参数，或在 Web 服务器层面对 counter.exe 的输入参数长度进行限制（如限制 URL 参数不超过 1024 字节），亦可迁移至其他受支持的网站计数器替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92713790426690&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92707671717292&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/267","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1031","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1031.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hmhc-wx7p-hg6x/GHSA-hmhc-wx7p-hg6x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/267/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0886.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0884","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0884.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1029","title":"SSH Communications Security sshd2 密码暴力破解漏洞","description":"SSH服务器sshd2 2.0.12之前版本存在认证记录缺失漏洞。当攻击者在达到最大尝试次数前主动关闭连接，服务端未能正确记录此次登录尝试，导致暴力破解行为不会出现在审计日志中。远程攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过审计机制，通过大量密码枚举尝试获取系统访问权限，严重影响系统安全性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1029"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.427","remediation":"升级 sshd2 至 2.0.12 或更高版本，该版本已正确记录所有登录尝试次数。同时可配置系统日志审计、部署 fail2ban 等暴力破解防护工具，并限制 SSH 登录尝试频率与来源 IP，增强暴力破解检测能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92663402004280&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/277","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2193","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1029","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1029.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6mfv-3x79-9r84/GHSA-6mfv-3x79-9r84.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/277/info.html","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-223.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0884.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0882","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0882.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0603","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 用户组成员权限配置不当漏洞","description":"在 Windows NT 系统中，用户账户可能被不当添加到高权限用户组（如 Administrators、Backup Operators、Domain Admins 等），导致低权限用户意外获得超出预期的系统访问权限。该漏洞源于系统组策略配置缺陷或管理失误，攻击者可利用已获取的低权限账户通过提权操作完全控制目标系统，影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0603"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.093","remediation":"立即审查所有域控制器和成员服务器上 Administrators、Backup Operators、Domain Admins、Power Users 等高权限组的成员列表，移除非必要或未授权的用户账户。通过「管理工具 → 计算机管理 → 本地用户和组 → 组」逐一检查各组成员，确保仅保留最小必要权限。部署安全基线策略（如 Microsoft Security Compliance Toolkit），定期审计组成员变更日志，并启用 Windows 审核策略中的「组成员管理」事件审计。升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本以利用细化的权限委派机制（如委派控制向导），避免将普通用户加入内置特权组。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0603","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0603","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0882.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0881","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0881.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0602","title":"多厂商网络入侵检测系统IP碎片重组绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理碎片化IP数据包时存在重组缺陷，攻击者可通过发送特制的碎片数据包绕过IDS检测规则。由于IDS无法正确还原原始载荷，恶意流量被误判为正常，导致攻击行为逃逸检测。该漏洞影响多种主流IDS产品，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用，且攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互。利用方式包括发送超小碎片、重叠偏移或超时碎片等绕过技术。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0602"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.983","remediation":"升级 IDS/IPS 引擎至最新版本（如 Snort ≥2.9.20、Suricata ≥7.0），启用 frag3 预处理器的分片重组功能；配置 `preprocessor frag3_global: max_frags 65536` 和 `preprocessor frag3_engine: policy windows`；对于无法升级的旧版系统，在网络层启用分片包拦截策略，仅允许完整 IP 包进入检测引擎。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0602","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0602.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8cxh-9x8c-5qr7/GHSA-8cxh-9x8c-5qr7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86251/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0881.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0880","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0880.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0601","title":"通用 网络入侵检测系统 TCP握手数据绕过漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0601 为网络入侵检测系统（IDS）中存在的TCP数据包处理缺陷。攻击者可在TCP三次握手过程中，将恶意载荷嵌入SYN、SYN-ACK等握手数据包的载荷字段或利用IP分片重组绕过IDS的深度包检测机制。由于早期IDS对TCP会话建立阶段的数据包缺乏完整重组与检测能力，导致攻击载荷可绕过安全审计直接到达目标主机。该漏洞影响了多种主流IDS产品的检测有效性，攻击者无需认证即可实施绕过，危害网络层面的安全监控体系。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0601"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.863","remediation":"启用 IDS/IPS 的 TCP 流重组功能（如 Snort 的 stream_tcp 预处理器或 Suricata 的内置流引擎），配置为自动重组所有 TCP 会话的完整载荷后再进行规则匹配；同时启用 TCP 规范化（normalization）以丢弃重叠分片或异常标志位的数据包，防止分片逃逸攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0601","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0601.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-45cf-cf6g-j6mm/GHSA-45cf-cf6g-j6mm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86244/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0880.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0879","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0600","title":"网络入侵检测系统 数据包校验和未验证漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理网络数据包时未验证校验和字段的正确性，远程攻击者可通过发送精心构造的畸形数据包绕过 IDS 的检测规则。由于 IDS 与目标主机对数据包的解析结果不一致，攻击者可利用该缺陷隐藏恶意流量，实现绕过告警的入侵行为。该漏洞影响多数未实现校验和验证的 IDS 产品，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0600"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.743","remediation":"在 IDS/IPS 配置中启用 IP 和 TCP 校验和验证功能（如 Snort 的 `config checksum_mode: all`），丢弃校验和错误的报文；升级至支持完整校验和检测的现代 IDS 版本（如 Suricata 7.x 或 Snort 3.x）；在边界防火墙上启用 TCP 校验和强制检查；同时在网络设备上启用 IP 选项过滤和分片重组校验，消除攻击者利用校验和绕过检测的路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0600","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0600.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86246/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0878","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0878.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0599","title":"通用 网络入侵检测系统 TCP异常序列号绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理包含异常TCP序列号的数据包时存在逻辑缺陷，攻击者可通过向目标网络发送精心构造的异常序列号数据包绕过IDS的检测与重组机制，导致恶意流量无法被正确识别和告警。该漏洞影响多种主流IDS产品，攻击者无需认证即可远程实施绕过攻击，严重削弱网络安全监控与威胁检测的有效性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0599"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.620","remediation":"升级支持 TCP 流重组（stream reassembly）的入侵检测系统，如 Suricata、Zeek（原名 Bro），并启用 `stream.reassembly` 引擎；禁用纯包级检测的旧式 IDS（如 Snort 1.x 传统模式）。配置 IDS 确保 TCP 分片重组策略与受保护目标主机一致（如设置 `target-based` 策略），避免插包（insertion）和逃逸（evasion）攻击。定期更新检测规则集以覆盖已知逃逸技术。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0599","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0599.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cgq4-92x7-335m/GHSA-cgq4-92x7-335m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86252/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0878.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0877","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0877.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1024","title":"LBL Tcpdump 3.4 ip_print 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"tcpdump 3.4a 及更早版本中的 ip_print 函数存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的零长度头部数据包，当 tcpdump 解析并打印该数据包时，会触发无限循环导致核心转储，从而使服务崩溃。该漏洞影响运行 tcpdump 3.4a 的系统，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1024"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-11-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.747","remediation":"升级到 tcpdump 3.4a7 及以上版本，该版本已移除导致死循环的递归 ip_print 调用。临时缓解措施：使用 tcpdump -s 24 限制抓包长度，或在内核层面添加 iptables 规则丢弃协议 4（IPIP）的异常报文。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92955903802773&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92963447601748&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92989907627051&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/313","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19251","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1024","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1024.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4xf9-whrj-cqwc/GHSA-4xf9-whrj-cqwc.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/313/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_151700_151800.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a2475725-573a-44a3-9fee-e5b8ed92fad2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0877.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0876","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0876.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0598","title":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）数据包乱序处理绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理乱序数据包时存在缺陷，无法正确重组和检测经过分片或乱序传输的攻击流量。远程攻击者可通过将恶意负载分散到多个乱序数据包中绕过 IDS 的检测规则，从而逃避安全监控。该漏洞影响多款主流网络入侵检测系统，可被用于隐藏端口扫描、漏洞利用等恶意行为，降低网络防御体系的有效性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0598"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.500","remediation":"配置IDS启用完整的TCP流重组（stream reassembly）功能，确保对乱序IP分片和TCP乱序报文进行正确重组后再执行规则匹配。同时启用分片超时与重组缓冲区限制，防止分片洪水绕过检测。建议使用支持应用层协议解析的现代IDS/IPS（如Snort/Suricata）并开启`stream5`或`stream`预处理模块。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0598","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0598.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hhgq-6w2j-9rc7/GHSA-hhgq-6w2j-9rc7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86249/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0876.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0875","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0875.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1023","title":"Sun Solaris useradd 账户过期日期绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 useradd 命令在解析 \"-e\"（账户过期日期）参数时，未能正确处理特定日期格式，当系统管理员或具有相应权限的用户使用某些非常规日期格式设置账户过期时间时，useradd 会错误地忽略或误解该设置，导致账户在过期后仍可正常登录系统。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需拥有本地账户并利用特定的日期格式参数即可绕过账户过期限制，获取非授权系统访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1023"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.613","remediation":"建议升级到 Solaris 8 或更高版本以彻底修复该问题。如无法升级，按 Sun 官方提供的解决方案替换 /etc/datemsk 配置文件，增加 %m/%d/%Y 等四位数年份格式（大写 %Y）使 useradd -e 能正确解析\"2000\"等四位年份，避免将 6/30/2000 误判为 2020 年。另外在创建账户后手动用 `logins -x` 验证到期日期是否正确，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92904175406756&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/426","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1023","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1023.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/solaris7_110869.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mc67-m38f-vc3q/GHSA-mc67-m38f-vc3q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/solaris7_x86_110870.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/426/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0875.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0874","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0874.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0597","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 账户策略登录时间限制绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 账户策略存在安全漏洞，当远程用户的登录时间到期后，系统未能强制断开其与服务器的连接，导致用户可在授权时段外继续访问系统资源。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，拥有有效域账户的远程攻击者可利用此问题绕过登录时间限制，在非授权时段持续访问服务器资源，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0597"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.383","remediation":"在 Windows NT 域用户管理器中选择\"规则(Policies)→账户(Account)\"，勾选\"当登录时数到期时强制断开远程用户与服务器的连接(Forcibly disconnect remote users from server when logon hours expire)\"。对于仍运行 Windows NT 的系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本，新版本默认启用该策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0597","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0597.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v2p7-wqpp-8h67/GHSA-v2p7-wqpp-8h67.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86258/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0874.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0873","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0873.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1019","title":"Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 5.0 的 SpectroSERVER 组件在安装时设置了不安全的目录权限，导致本地攻击者可将该目录中的特权可执行文件 processd 替换为特洛伊木马。成功利用该漏洞的攻击者可获得 root 或 Administrator 权限，完全控制目标系统。漏洞利用要求攻击者拥有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1019"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.087","remediation":"立即修改 Spectrum Enterprise Manager 安装目录（默认路径通常为 /opt/Spectrum 或 C:\\Program Files\\Cabletron\\Spectrum）及其子目录的权限，确保仅 root/Administrator 具有写入权限，普通用户仅保留读取与执行权限；使用 chmod 755 或更严格的权限设置。同时校验 processd 可执行文件的完整性（比对 md5/sha256 哈希值），若发现被替换则从原始安装介质恢复。作为长远方案，建议迁移至仍在维护的网络管理平台。服务器层面配置文件完整性监控（如 Tripwire 或 AIDE），对 processd 等关键二进制文件进行实时变更告警。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93024398513475&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93024398713491&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/495","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1019","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1019.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3523-w4qj-m836/GHSA-3523-w4qj-m836.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0873.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0872","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0596","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 日志文件大小与保留期限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 日志文件的最大大小或保留期限配置不当，可能导致日志文件无限制增长耗尽磁盘空间，引发拒绝服务；或日志过早轮转覆盖，导致关键安全事件记录丢失，影响事后审计与取证分析。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0596"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.267","remediation":"建议在 Windows NT 事件查看器中右键「事件日志」→「日志设置」，将日志最大大小根据磁盘容量设为 512MB 以上，回卷策略设为「按需要覆盖事件」而非「不要覆盖事件」。若仍使用旧版系统，应升级至 Windows Server 2003 及以上版本以获得完善的日志审计功能。作为临时缓解措施，可设置组策略定期归档并清理旧日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0596","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0596.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x2q8-w843-gwx7/GHSA-x2q8-w843-gwx7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86256/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml"}]